issue.title: Batch jobs cannot read source file in group chats
Batch jobs cannot read source file in group chats

comment.body: This is a configuration issue. To allow the bot to see group messages not starting with '/', disable privacy mode through `/setprivacy`. The bot will have to be re-added for the change to take effect.
